Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:12.48,IN-JP_EP01_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}オナジキモチ!!{（⸝⸝＞▿＜⸝⸝）}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:15.07,IN-JP_EP01_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}繋がってる　実感
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:17.57,IN-JP_EP01_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}分け合う　温もり　ありがとう
