Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.71,0:20:39.48,IN-JP_EP01_M2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I Mean…No More Hiding ダ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.20,0:20:45.72,IN-JP_EP01_M2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Changing…So I’m Trying Now
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.27,0:19:16.28,IN-CH_EP01_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}心情愉悅！
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.28,0:19:18.06,IN-CH_EP01_M2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}開心到飛起！
